WEBVTT

00:02:21.520 --> 00:02:23.759
From the main hall to Master Liu's courtyard,

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:25.319
this is the shortest path.

00:02:26.919 --> 00:02:29.159
If the killer is among us,

00:02:29.599 --> 00:02:31.759
then how did he manage to so quickly

00:02:31.759 --> 00:02:32.680
go back and forth?

00:02:39.319 --> 00:02:40.159
Wheel tracks.

00:03:07.080 --> 00:03:07.759
Divine Doctor Du.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:09.599
What's wrong?

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:11.000
Someone is following me.

00:03:12.520 --> 00:03:13.199
Watch out.

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:21.000
Let's go.

00:03:37.039 --> 00:03:37.800
Miss Xiao Bai.

00:03:40.120 --> 00:03:41.039
Why come to the Myriad Treasures Pavilion?

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:43.599
The villa's best medicine

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:45.400
is not in the pharmacy,

00:03:45.879 --> 00:03:46.759
it's all here.

00:03:47.879 --> 00:03:48.520
Okay.

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:49.560
I'll apply the medicine for you.

00:03:54.319 --> 00:03:54.879
Pardon me.

00:04:14.439 --> 00:04:15.680
It hurts.

00:04:18.439 --> 00:04:19.480
Ye Li.

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:20.920
Zhao Yun.

00:04:20.920 --> 00:04:21.839
I'm in so much pain.

00:04:38.439 --> 00:04:39.240
Done.

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:45.079
Thank you, Divine Doctor Du.

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:48.839
What is it?

00:04:52.519 --> 00:04:53.160
Nothing.

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:06.319
Recorded here is

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:10.439
the guest list for the annual All-Knowing Night Banquet.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.000
I don't know either.

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:14.639
I'm just a maid in the Young Miss's room.

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:18.120
I'm not qualified to serve the banquet guests.

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:23.639
Since guests do business at the banquet,

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.519
the transactions should also be recorded.

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:28.000
Why is only the transaction date written here,

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.600
but not the price or the buyer?

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:33.639
The Villa Master started as an accountant.

00:05:34.519 --> 00:05:35.720
He has a habit of keeping accounts.

00:05:37.879 --> 00:05:39.600
Could he have recorded it in a ledger?

00:05:41.319 --> 00:05:43.680
When I saw the accounting office balancing books,

00:05:44.040 --> 00:05:45.360
they carried boxes like that.

00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:49.160
I'll help you over there.

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:55.439
Someone's coming.

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:56.240
Hide behind me.

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:46.199
You...

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:47.279
Are you...

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:48.680
crying from pain?

00:06:49.279 --> 00:06:50.279
Or crying from fear?

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:52.399
It hurts,

00:06:53.399 --> 00:06:54.279
and I'm scared too.

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:04.040
It's okay now.

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:10.439
I'm afraid that person will come back.

00:07:11.439 --> 00:07:12.560
Let's leave here first.

00:07:16.079 --> 00:07:17.199
You're not looking for the ledger anymore?

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:19.839
I will.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:21.839
I'll find someone to look for me.

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:32.720
Did you see clearly what that person looked like?

00:07:32.879 --> 00:07:33.399
No.

00:07:34.399 --> 00:07:35.800
It's likely the killer.

00:07:36.199 --> 00:07:37.560
He doesn't want us to keep investigating.

00:07:39.040 --> 00:07:41.319
I feel that the Villa Master, Master Liu,

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:42.759
Zhang Shan's death,

00:07:43.839 --> 00:07:44.720
and this villa...

00:07:45.519 --> 00:07:47.279
must be hiding unspeakable secrets.

00:07:49.839 --> 00:07:50.800
In short,

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:52.160
it's not that simple.

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:54.639
Master Kun, telling me this...

00:07:55.240 --> 00:07:56.959
does it mean you agree to let me investigate with you?

00:07:59.240 --> 00:08:00.439
Where is the ledger you mentioned?

00:08:04.959 --> 00:08:05.839
Myriad Treasures Pavilion.

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:07.920
But before finding the ledger,

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:09.759
I need to borrow something from you first.

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:12.920
What is it?

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:15.360
Your authority.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:37.320
You!

00:08:37.679 --> 00:08:38.720
What is wrong with you?

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:39.519
You didn't knock.

00:08:39.519 --> 00:08:40.559
Make some noise, will you?

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:44.399
Master Kun.

00:08:44.559 --> 00:08:45.720
Why are you here too?

00:08:46.799 --> 00:08:48.240
When you were eating,

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:49.960
what did you use to pick the lock?

00:08:52.919 --> 00:08:53.799
Don't spread rumors.

00:08:53.919 --> 00:08:54.799
I am a law-abiding citizen.

00:08:55.279 --> 00:08:56.600
Things like picking locks and breaking in,

00:08:56.759 --> 00:08:57.720
I can't do that, no way.

00:08:58.159 --> 00:08:59.080
No way, no way.

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:00.960
Is that so?

00:09:06.159 --> 00:09:06.919
Then,

00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:11.080
what is this?

00:09:12.159 --> 00:09:12.840
Please have some tea.

00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:13.799
I'll do it myself.

00:09:14.559 --> 00:09:15.759
Watch what you're doing!

00:09:24.440 --> 00:09:25.600
This... this...

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:27.240
It's a token of love!

00:09:28.159 --> 00:09:28.919
Is that strange?

00:09:29.799 --> 00:09:30.320
Is it strange?

00:09:31.519 --> 00:09:32.720
Having a comb isn't strange.

00:09:33.799 --> 00:09:35.799
But this rhinoceros horn material...

00:09:38.279 --> 00:09:39.679
is an Imperial tribute.

00:09:39.679 --> 00:09:42.440
I wonder which noble family Sister-in-law is from?

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:45.480
Officer.

00:09:45.840 --> 00:09:46.480
How about...

00:09:46.600 --> 00:09:48.399
for the sake of me helping you cover up your lie,

00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:49.559
just let me off this time?

00:09:49.720 --> 00:09:50.080
Okay?

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:51.399
Right.

00:09:51.759 --> 00:09:52.360
Those twenty taels...

00:09:52.519 --> 00:09:53.679
I don't want them anymore. No, no.

00:09:54.799 --> 00:09:55.799
Consider it my tribute to you, my lord.

00:09:56.000 --> 00:09:57.039
How did you know

00:09:57.759 --> 00:09:58.559
that I am an officer?

00:10:01.039 --> 00:10:02.519
If you weren't an officer,

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.639
how would you recognize this Imperial tribute?

00:10:11.159 --> 00:10:12.279
Since a crime was committed,

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:14.840
there is absolutely no reason to be lenient.

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:17.399
However,

00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:20.000
you could atone for your crimes with good deeds.

00:10:21.720 --> 00:10:22.240
I can.

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:23.759
I can, I can.

00:10:38.879 --> 00:10:39.759
You really are an expert.

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:44.679
One stack for each of us.

00:10:46.879 --> 00:10:47.600
If we look at it this way,

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:49.480
aren't we all on the same side now?

00:10:50.120 --> 00:10:51.000
Get to work.

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:56.600
Since you are an Officer,

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:57.840
then what about you?

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.080
You aren't really a prisoner, are you?

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.000
Shut up.

00:11:03.159 --> 00:11:05.559
An Officer bringing a prisoner to investigate a case...

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:07.440
that's interesting.

00:11:08.159 --> 00:11:09.320
Shut up.

00:11:25.840 --> 00:11:26.759
Why do you keep coughing?

00:11:28.559 --> 00:11:29.200
Can't help it.

00:11:29.559 --> 00:11:30.200
I suffer from a cold ailment.

00:11:31.799 --> 00:11:32.240
Look.

00:11:42.559 --> 00:11:44.000
One sheep for eight thousand gold.

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:45.960
Gold.

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:49.360
What kind of sheep

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:50.200
sells for that much?

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:54.840
That reminds me of something.

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:55.679
Speak.

00:11:56.279 --> 00:11:57.639
One tael of silver.

00:12:04.039 --> 00:12:04.799
Consider it a loan.

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:05.840
I'll pay you back if I get out alive.

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:12.840
Can you speak now?

00:12:15.240 --> 00:12:17.000
Those of us who roam the Jianghu...

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:18.039
all know that

00:12:18.799 --> 00:12:19.799
in the black market,

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:21.840
humans aren't called humans.

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:23.879
They're called Two-legged Sheep.

00:12:24.840 --> 00:12:26.960
If you want to buy "sheep" in this black market,

00:12:27.279 --> 00:12:28.200
you have to use gold.

00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:30.840
It seems this villa

00:12:31.360 --> 00:12:32.679
is still trafficking humans.

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:33.799
No wonder

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:35.679
none of these servants show their faces.

00:12:36.279 --> 00:12:36.759
Wait.

00:12:38.639 --> 00:12:39.919
When Master Liu died,

00:12:40.679 --> 00:12:42.679
"Cause and Effect" was written on the wall.

00:12:43.879 --> 00:12:45.720
What kind of Cause and Effect is it?

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:49.279
Could it be the cause Master Liu created

00:12:49.799 --> 00:12:50.840
became the effect of his murder?

00:12:52.039 --> 00:12:53.279
You'd have to ask Master Liu that.

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:56.320
The dead naturally cannot speak.

00:12:56.519 --> 00:12:57.159
But,

00:12:59.559 --> 00:13:00.279
the living can.

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:05.399
Something happened!

00:13:05.600 --> 00:13:06.159
What?

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:07.039
Don't ask.

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:07.759
Hurry, let's go.